          "content": "Supplier Contract SC-88\n\nBuyer: SEMAA Marine Operations\nSupplier: OceanCore Parts Ltd.\nContract Start: 2026-01-01\nContract End: 2026-12-31\n\nScope\n- Monthly delivery of cooling pump filters.\n- Priority support for overheating incidents.\n\nService Levels\n- Standard delivery: within 5 business days.\n- Emergency delivery: within 24 hours after approved request.\n\nCommercial Terms\n- Unit price for filter model CPF-9: USD 220.\n- Bulk discount applies for orders above 200 units per month.\n- Late delivery penalty: 2 percent invoice deduction per delayed day, capped at 20 percent.\n\nContract Contacts\n- SEMAA contact: Brian Wu\n- Supplier contact: Julia Park\n\nTermination\n- Buyer may terminate with 30-day notice for repeated SLA breach.\n- Immediate termination allowed for falsified quality certification.",
